{{!
    @template core/email_html

    Template for all html emails. Note that it may wrap content formatted
    elsewhere in another a module template.

    Context variables required for this template:
    * sitefullname
    * siteshortname
    * sitewwwroot
    * subject
    * to
    * toname
    * touserid
    * tousername
    * from
    * fromname
    * replyto
    * replytoname
    * body

    Example context (json):
    {
        "body": "Email body"
    }
}}
